claims:
4. A method for establishing a metastatic renal cell carcinoma miRNA expression signature comprising:
determining a plurality of miRNA expression levels in one or more tumor tissue samples from a cohort of subjects;
performing a univariate logistic regression analysis to identify a set of one or more miRNAs associated with metastasis;
assigning a risk score to each tumor tissue sample by calculating a risk score formula; and
determining a cut-off risk score to stratify the cohort subjects into one or more risk groups.
